{"tid":908791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係中產、有錢人角度，香港有冇自由又點","createTime":"2018-11-20T00:21:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T05:16:14.000Z","uid":19932,"like":37,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"255813f8210b864e100a5b271db4b48d9024ed76","tid":908791,"uid":19932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T00:21:50.000Z","msg":"唔好住就搬，一放假就飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算要翻工、打理生意，都可以隨時放棄，唔會影響生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n民生？翻放工揸車，最多堵車麻煩啲，地鐵係點都未知。同林鄭連八達通都唔識用一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n醫生律師放假唔係去旅行就屋企hea足一日，深水埗元朗蝻禍根本未知發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 商場唔高級唔行。<br />\n更加唔好話蝗禍，係佢地心目中就係揾錢機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 藥房金行水魚，搞佔中就係垃圾廢青。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廣東話收皮就收皮，仔女係外國讀書，分分鐘廣東話都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲鼓勵仔女學普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n簡單啲講，香港係有錢佬福地，窮人地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e4dfd8c1ed3501d99d5d8f5161a5c01a6ddcbd","tid":908791,"uid":19932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T00:49:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fe849492be6848e3723519b1a1c8e2757b94967","tid":908791,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T00:54:57.000Z","msg":"好酸呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9779eafd550678a262b16f0b077051ca5519be","tid":908791,"uid":192068,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T00:55:30.000Z","msg":"而家美國放吓風已經嚇到傻左<br />\n香港出事佢地唔會獨善其身㗎"},{"pid":"7ddc66932443e837c3204c442524951f9bf1f63e","tid":908791,"uid":59848,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"ci